  "description": "A close-up photograph captures a vibrant scene of a garden in bright sunlight. The dominant element is lush greenery consisting of broad, textured leaves, suggesting a plant with large foliage.  Interspersed among the leaves are delicate clusters of small, bright blue flowers.  A butterfly, with orange and brown patterned wings, is perched delicately on one of the flower clusters, seemingly feeding. The background is blurred, revealing hints of brown earth and other vegetation, creating a shallow depth of field that emphasizes the foreground elements. The lighting casts strong shadows, highlighting the textures of the leaves and the butterfly\u2019s wings.",
